87
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,640
he needed me,

88
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,660
and I had to help him through this.

89
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,720
Later,

90
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,920
we won the competition together

91
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,570
and saved 'Old Dreams'.

92
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,600
With his help,

93
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,200
I finally dared to face

94
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,040
the person I was on stage.

95
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,040
I knew

96
