I wanted to perform opera.

97
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,360
As we were moving toward each other,

98
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,960
as I increasingly believed

99
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,880
that this person was truly

100
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,600
my destined one,

101
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,480
I unexpectedly

102
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,200
discovered the truth.

103
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,080
You

104
