Listen.

106
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,740
You didn't do anything wrong.

107
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,600
Then I...

108
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,800
Then why?

109
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,120
Your mistake was...

110
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,160
The person you wanted to kill

111
