and leave Haicheng.

114
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,840
Now I know the whole truth.

115
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,320
On my wedding day,

116
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,860
I want to unmask him with my own hands.

117
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,200
Let everyone know

118
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,840
who the real murderer is.

119
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,840
I thought I was marrying my perfect match.

120
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,120
Little did I know

121
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:54,800
he would be so cruel beneath his facade.

122
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,920
Why?

123
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,000
What are you doing?

124
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,280
I'm seeking justice for myself,

125
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:09,050
clearing the names of those wrongfully accused,

126
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:13,050
and demanding justice for all who died unjustly.

127
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:21,040
Mr. Chen, what a brilliant turnaround performance!

128
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,840
Young Master, you're mistaken.

129
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,240
The play I just performed

130
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,610
is called 'Old Dreams'.

131
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:37,919
Nonsense!

132
