This isn't 'Old Dreams' at all.

133
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,880
Guards!

134
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,120
Arrest these actors who are

135
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,440
spreading dangerous lies!

136
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,280
Nobody move!

137
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,840
Look carefully.

138
00:08:56,560 --> 00:09:00,490
This is the 'Old Dreams' manuscript you've been desperately seeking.

139
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,160
You will never

140
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,160
get it.

141
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,560
Impossible.

142
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,280
It can't be.

143
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,200
What my master passed down to me

144
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,130
