145
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,570
That's impossible.

146
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,560
It was you.

147
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,920
You switched it.

148
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,080
No.

149
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:40,800
It was Lu Shun.

150
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:45,080
He never intended to pass 'Old Dreams' to you.

151
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,080
He didn't want me to have it.

152
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,640
Tell me.

153
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,960
Where have you hidden 'Old Dreams'?

154
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,640
I told you.

155
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,680
This is 'Old Dreams'.

156
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,960
Nonsense!

157
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,120
How could I not know what 'Old Dreams' is?

158
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,520
Of course you don't know.

159
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,280
From the moment you abandoned Mule Society

160
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:11,400
and broke with your master,

161
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,640
you were destined

162
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:16,480
to never understand what 'Old Dreams' truly means.

163
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,840
To obtain it,

164
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:21,010
you've committed countless atrocities.

165
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:24,080
You established the Opera Guild to win over the wealthy

166
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:26,680
while exploiting and persecuting your peers.

167
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,960
You used the opera troupe

168
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:31,690
to launder money and embezzle military funds for Commander Zhang.

169
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,040
And Commander Zhang

170
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,120
naturally became

171
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,760
your biggest backer in both legal and criminal worlds.

172
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,840
Shut up!

173
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,360
When I saw that the script

174
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,410
had not a single word written in it,

175
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,720
I finally understood

176
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,200
why my master

177
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:55,120
wanted me to wait five years before opening it.

178
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,610
He wanted to tell me that

179
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:03,490
while theater is indeed the foundation of Mule Society,

180
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,160
theater comes from life.

181
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,080
Each of us has

182
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,840
our own 'Old Dreams.'

183
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,600
It's something that can only be written

184
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,600
after experiencing life yourself.

185
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:20,680
He Zhen.

186
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,160
You originally

187
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,800
had your own copy of 'Old Dreams'.

188
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,800
Nonsense!

189
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,880
Guards!

190
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,520
Arrest this woman

191
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:45,560
who spreads lies.

192
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:46,600
Wait.

193
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:49,640
Young Commander.

194
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,960
Don't listen to that woman's nonsense.

195
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,960
I've been loyal to your father

196
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,560
and to you all along.

197
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:59,370
I've been wholeheartedly helping you manage Haicheng.

198
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:03,060
You don't actually believe what that actress says, do you?

199
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,200
Colonel Zhang.

200
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,160
Actually, all these years,

201
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,840
my father knew everything

202
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,600
you've done in Haicheng.

203
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,280
He just spared you

204
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,640
out of old friendship.

205
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,000
But I'm not my father.

206
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:22,100
I've already collected evidence of your wrongdoings.

207
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:25,380
I've just been waiting for the right moment.

208
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:28,320
I want to expose you

209
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,850
