217
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,120
I have nothing

218
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,080
to do with him. I...

219
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,600
Chen Zhiyi.

220
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,690
It's all your fault.

221
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:24,360
I'll strangle you, you little liar.

222
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,400
Senior, Zhiyi, Zhiyi.

223
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:39,090
I've been waiting for this moment for a long time.

224
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,440
Don't you have anything to say to me?

225
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:31,920
Fine.

226
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:35,080
So sister went to all this trouble

227
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,560
