229
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:43,250
But what difference does it make that you're standing here?

230
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,880
Don't forget who you are.

231
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,160
You're still a murderer.

232
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,480
You bastard.

233
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:53,410
