234
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:58,360
These are the white gloves I found on Dalin.

235
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,800
A pair of white gloves from who knows where.

236
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,000
What does that prove?

237
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:06,600
I have many pairs of gloves like these.

238
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,680
If you like them, I can give you a pair.

239
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,760
You've always been careful,

240
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:13,040
but you made two fatal mistakes.

241
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:16,100
Dalin's hands were larger than others',

242
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:19,120
so only he could wear these gloves.

243
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,280
So what?

244
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:24,120
So you met him before he died,

245
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,800
you fought with him,

246
00:15:26,040 --> 00:15:27,440
