249
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:35,440
Dalin seemed careless on the surface,

250
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:37,570
but he was actually quite meticulous.

251
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,160
Before he died,

252
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,820
with his last bit of strength,

253
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,000
he pressed that bullet casing

254
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,800
into your narcissus flower bed.

255
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,640
This finger

256
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:49,240
with its indentation

257
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:51,080
is the best evidence.

258
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:55,440
