260
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,800
That's your second mistake:

261
00:15:59,040 --> 00:16:00,120
overconfidence.

262
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,720
Because of your confidence,

263
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:05,220
you didn't notice the white gloves on Dalin.

264
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,640
Because of your confidence,

265
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:08,720
you didn't check

266
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:10,360
before bringing the narcissus flowers for Zhiyi

267
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,440
to the He family.

268
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:19,120
So you married into the He family

269
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:20,800
and became my wife

270
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:23,560
just for this?

271
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,720
If I'm not mistaken,

272
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,500
that bullet casing

273
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:33,920
is buried in your daffodil field.

274
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,360
Buried alongside it

275
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:39,800
is also the old troupe leader of the Red Maple Opera,

276
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,200
Wan Fuming's body.

277
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,200
He Mingxu.

278
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:47,080
Dalin's fatal wound was from a gunshot.

279
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,640
Do you dare take off your shirt

280
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,840
and let everyone see?

281
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,760
If your wound matches Dalin's,

282
00:16:51,760 --> 00:16:53,220
then you are the murderer.

283
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,640
He Mingxu.

284
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,640
Do as he says.

285
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:43,240
You told me

286
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:45,760
when I missed you,

287
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,920
